    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for this absolute gem. It\u2019s been a fantastic, reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape, just waiting for its next adventure! Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is ready to get you there in comfort. It\u2019s been well-loved and runs beautifully\u2014come by and see for yourself why I\u2019ve enjoyed driving it so much!",
