      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the ideal balance between everyday utility and premium comfort. The exterior retains a beautiful finish, with only minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the leather upholstery is soft and free of tears, and all electronic features\u2014including the dual-zone climate control and premium sound system\u2014operate exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is in great shape, having received regular synthetic oil changes and a recent multi-point inspection. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension provides a composed, quiet ride. It comes with a full set of floor mats, two sets of keys, and a clean title. This is a turnkey opportunity for a buyer who values a vehicle that has been treated with respect and is ready for many more miles of reliable service.",
      "price": 34850.0,
