      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride and it has been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me every single day. It runs beautifully and is totally ready for its next big adventure! This is the perfect find for someone who wants a dependable, well-loved car that still looks great on the road. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
