    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The mechanical vitals are robust, with a recently performed valve shim adjustment and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure optimal cam timing. The chassis has been addressed with rear subframe reinforcement, mitigating the common E46 floor-pan fatigue. It retains its factory M-Variable limited-slip differential for precise power delivery out of corners. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the suspension geometry remains true, benefiting from refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. This is a mechanically sorted machine optimized for performance and longevity.",
